query: SELECT e.id as enrollment_id, e.bundleId, b.id as bundle_id, b.name as bundle_name, CASE WHEN b.id IS NULL THEN 'NO MATCH' ELSE 'MATCH' END as match_status FROM course_enrollments e LEFT JOIN course_bundles b ON e.bundleId = b.id WHERE e.bundleId IS NOT NULL LIMIT 10;
